name: Foundation for Entrepreneurship Development of Orissa (FEDO)
briefDescription: Vocational training information and project partnerships.Foundation for Entrepreneurship Development of Orissa is a non-profit making, non-political and non- government organization in the state committed for enabling self help and enhancing livelihoods of deprived rural, urban and tribal communities integrating micro-finance and micro entrepreneurship cultures in the process of stimulatory, support and sustaining socio economic activities in Orissa since 1990.
